name: Saint Judah//The Third
description:
Half Saint series,
#III of XII

Illegal clinic doctor
Good hearted traitor
Chaotic Neutral

"Hailed from the land that has long forgotten its name
 Discovering new idea of home at the edge of the world
 In his fingers, a power to sustain life
 A savior for those whom the idea of home is only suffering
 Perpetrated by the covenant who warrant salvation
 A covenant that once gave him the coveted idea of home."

[The Lost Proverb of Saints, Chapter XIV: Judah, The Third]
